# 기술 스택

## Frontend + Backend
- **Framework:** Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript (strict)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **Server Logic:** Server Actions + Route Handlers

## Database
- Prisma ORM + SQLite (로컬 전용)

## AI / OCR
- Google Gemini 1.5 Pro Vision (Vercel AI SDK)

## RPA
- Puppeteer + puppeteer-extra + stealth plugin
- node-cron (헬스체크 스케줄러)

## 문서/이미지/엑셀
- sharp (이미지 변환), pdf-lib (PDF), exceljs (엑셀), Resend (이메일)

## 보안
- AES-256-GCM (계정 암호화), SHA-256 (캡처 해싱)
